

                Romanceiro Folclorico do Brasil
                ===============================


                     Rossini Tavares de Lima



       Copyright 1971 by IRMAOS VITALE S/A.  Ind. e Com.
              - Sao Paulo - Rio de Janeiro - Brasil.

   Todos os direitos autorais reservados para todos os paises
                      All rights reserved.

                             19-L
                         IRMAOS VITALE
                            EDITORES
                             BRASIL

                               |             
                               |             


This work chronicles eight Brazilian romantic ballads.
For each romance, there are several variants documented
in the book.  Only the variants that are accompanied by
musical notation have been encoded in this electronic
collection.

The Romances include the following:

       	Antoniho                       6 variants
       	Cego Ou Ceguinho              10 variants
       	Conde da Alemanha              2 variants
       	Costureira Ou Modista          6 variants
       	Donzela                        5 variants
       	Juliana E D. Jorge            23 variants
       	Santa Helena Ou Iria           4 variants
       	Silvaninha                     7 variants

An additional 24 documents under 11 Romances are available
in the book, but are not included in this distribution.

Most tunes are similar for a given Romance, but some
Romances exhibit two or more contrasting musical settings.

Given the large number of variants, this database lends
itself especially well to the study of musical variation.

